summary: Recolored armor i made for my game.
descriptionHtml:
Just removed green/yellow to have it look.. i dunno, but fits my guy better.
It\'s not a big thing, just colors removed, still figured i\'d share if anyone wants to use it.
Ok.. \'bout it. Have fun ;)

PS: Names a joke, girls look good in it too , but seriously didn\'t know what to name it so just went with it.

PPS: Yeah grew bored with the joke name so now its Metalcolor
